        "additionalValue": null
      },
      {
        "featureType": "DIGITAL_BANKING",
        "additionalInfo": "Just another way you can connect your money with your lifestyle. From banking easily on the go with the MyState Bank App, or at home through Internet Banking, to making faster payments with digital wallets or PayID, there are more ways than ever to access your money. Keeping your bank accounts safe is a key priority for us, so you can be confident starting today.",
